- content_for :css_each_page, stylesheet_link_tag('books')
nav.is-fixed-top.light-border-bottom.is-flex.push-side
  .control.has-icons-left.has-icons-right.is-flex.is-fluid.container.field
    = form_with url: search_path, method: :get, local: true, class: [:small_margin, :navbar_left] do |f|
      = f.text_field :title, class: 'input is-success', placeholder: '著書名', value: params[:title]
      span.icon.is-small.is-left.small_margin
        i.fas.fa-book
    = link_to root_path, id: "close-form", class: 'is-inline-block has-text-centered navbar_right header-line-hight'  do
      i.fas.fa-times
.hero-body
  p.has-text-weight-bold そくどく文庫は、本を読むのが遅い人でも楽に本を読む速度が早くなるサイトです📖
section.section
  .container
    .columns.is-mobile.is-multiline
      = render 'books/books', books: @books

sass:
  .small_margin
    margin-right: 0
